        Encapsulation
        =============

    -> The process of binding data members and corrosponding methods into a single unit is nothing but encapsulation.

        class Student{
            data members + methods (behaviours)
        }

    -> If any component follows data hiding and abstaction such type of component is said to be encapsulated component.

    -> Advantages of the encapsulation are we can achieve security, Enhancement will become easy, it improve maintainabilty of the applications.
    -> The main disadvantage of encapsulation is it increases length of the code and slows down execution.

    
